    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena sūriyo devaputto rāhunā asurindena gahito hoti. ",
          "en": "Now at that time the Sun God had been seized by Rāhu, lord of demons. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho sūriyo devaputto bhagavantaṃ anussaramāno tāyaṃ velāyaṃ imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then the Sun God, recollecting the Buddha, at that time recited this verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:2.1",
          "pli": "“Namo te buddha vīratthu, ",
          "en": "“Homage to you, Buddha, hero! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:2.2",
          "pli": "vippamuttosi sabbadhi; ",
          "en": "You’re freed in every way. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:2.3",
          "pli": "Sambādhapaṭipannosmi, ",
          "en": "I’ve wandered into confinement: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:2.4",
          "pli": "tassa me saraṇaṃ bhavā”ti. ",
          "en": "be my refuge!” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:3.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho bhagavā sūriyaṃ devaputtaṃ ārabbha rāhuṃ asurindaṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi: ",
          "en": "Then the Buddha addressed Rāhu in verse concerning the Sun God: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:4.1",
          "pli": "“Tathāgataṃ arahantaṃ, ",
          "en": "“The Sun God has gone for refuge "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:4.2",
          "pli": "sūriyo saraṇaṃ gato; ",
          "en": "to the Realized One, the perfected one. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:4.3",
          "pli": "Rāhu sūriyaṃ pamuñcassu, ",
          "en": "Rāhu, release the Sun! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:4.4",
          "pli": "buddhā lokānukampakā. ",
          "en": "Buddhas have compassion for the world! "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:5.1",
          "pli": "Yo andhakāre tamasi pabhaṅkaro, ",
          "en": "He fills the darkness with light, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:5.2",
          "pli": "Verocano maṇḍalī uggatejo; ",
          "en": "the shining sun, circle of magnificent flame. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:5.3",
          "pli": "Mā rāhu gilī caramantalikkhe, ",
          "en": "Rāhu, do not swallow him as he traverses the sky. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:5.4",
          "pli": "Pajaṃ mamaṃ rāhu pamuñca sūriyan”ti. ",
          "en": "Rāhu, release my progeny, the Sun!” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:6.1",
          "pli": "Atha kho rāhu asurindo sūriyaṃ devaputtaṃ muñcitvā taramānarūpo yena vepacitti asurindo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā saṃviggo lomahaṭṭhajāto ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. ",
          "en": "Then Rāhu, having released the Sun, rushed to see Vepacitti, lord of demons and stood to one side, shocked and awestruck. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:6.2",
          "pli": "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ kho rāhuṃ asurindaṃ vepacitti asurindo gāthāya ajjhabhāsi: ",
          "en": "Vepacitti addressed him in verse: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:7.1",
          "pli": "“Kiṃ nu santaramānova, ",
          "en": "“Why the rush? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:7.2",
          "pli": "rāhu sūriyaṃ pamuñcasi; ",
          "en": "Rāhu, you released the Sun "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:7.3",
          "pli": "Saṃviggarūpo āgamma, ",
          "en": "and came here looking like you’re in shock: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:7.4",
          "pli": "kiṃ nu bhītova tiṭṭhasī”ti. ",
          "en": "why do you stand there so scared?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:8.1",
          "pli": "“Sattadhā me phale muddhā, ",
          "en": "“My head would have exploded in seven pieces, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:8.2",
          "pli": "jīvanto na sukhaṃ labhe; ",
          "en": "I would have found no joy in life, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:8.3",
          "pli": "Buddhagāthābhigītomhi, ",
          "en": "if, when enchanted by the Buddha’s spell, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:8.4",
          "pli": "no ce muñceyya sūriyan”ti. ",
          "en": "I had not released the Sun.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:8.5",
          "pli": "Paṭhamo vaggo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:9.1",
          "pli": "Dve kassapā ca māgho ca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:9.2",
          "pli": "Māgadho dāmali kāmado; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:9.3",
          "pli": "Pañcālacaṇḍo tāyano, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn2.10:9.4",
          "pli": "Candimasūriyena te dasāti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
